data.description: Great home, 3/2.5, move in ready, conveniently located just outside of Altavista between Gretna and Lynchburg. Roof and windows replaced in 2018. Large backyard that is level. Extra large garage/workshop with concrecte floor and lean tube. Prefer 24 hour notice for showings and before 1pm would be great, if possible, owner works 3rd shift.
